ge-scale mines, large-scale mining concessions, unofficial small-scale mining concessions, and unsuitable small-scale mining areas.\n            </p>\n    </div>\n    <div>\n        <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 900px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 106.66666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"Figure 5\" title=\"Figure 5\" src=\"/static/cdebfff7cdf8c205593f92d527ff3a69/1cfc2/figure_5.png\" srcset=\"/static/cdebfff7cdf8c205593f92d527ff3a69/3684f/figure_5.png 225w,\n/static/cdebfff7cdf8c205593f92d527ff3a69/fc2a6/figure_5.png 450w,\n/static/cdebfff7cdf8c205593f92d527ff3a69/1cfc2/figure_5.png 900w,\n/static/cdebfff7cdf8c205593f92d527ff3a69/21482/figure_5.png 1350w,\n/static/cdebfff7cdf8c205593f92d527ff3a69/2643c/figure_5.png 1747w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n    </span>\n            <p>\n                <span style=\"font-weight: 600\">Figure 5:</span> Southwest region\n                of the study area shown with the small-scale mining (SSM) derived from the 2013 and 2015 Landsat-7 and -8 imagery in the context of the\n                surrounding cities, large-scale mines, large-scale mining concessions, unofficial small-scale mining concessions, and unsuitable small-scale mining areas.\n            </p>\n    </div>\n    <div>\n        <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 900px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 106.66666666666667%; position: relative; bot